SMTP protocol ka use kiya jata hai mail send karne ke liye
# Email Send Flow:

01. Sabse pehle project me mail bhejne ke liye dependency add ki gayi:
    javax.mail (mail dependency) pom.xml me add ki, aur system.properties me SMTP ke parameters set kiye.

02. Humne 3 custom classes banayi:
    - EmailMessage → email ka data hold karta hai (to, subject, message)
    - EmailUtility → mail send karne ka kaam karta hai
    - EmailBuilder → mail ka content (HTML message) banata hai

03. EmailBuilder class ka use karke mail ka message generate kiya jata hai:
    jaise getUserRegistrationMessage(), getForgetPasswordMessage(), getChangePasswordMessage().

04. EmailMessage class me mail ke attributes set kiye jate hain:
    - to (kisko mail bhejna hai)
    - subject
    - message (EmailBuilder se aaya hua content)

05. EmailUtility class me sendMail() method banayi gayi jisme actual mail send hota hai.


06. sendMail() method me JavaMail ki predefined classes ka use kiva jata hai (6 classes):
    - Session
    - Authenticator
    - PasswordAuthentication
    - Message
    - MimeMessage
    - Transport

07. Finally:
    Transport.send(msg) method call karke mail SMTP server ke through mail send kiya jata hai.
